<doc id="1079923" wikidata="Q5737171" url="?curid=1079923" title="Here Comes the Bride (album)">
<text>Here Comes the Bride is the fourth studio album by the American rock band Spin Doctors, released in 1999.

==Track listing==
==Personnel==
